Called customer service today to ask about our policy renewal notification, because my premium will be doubling, which I thought was a bit excessive.
The representative was less than helpful, telling me that all of the reasons are "very complicated and hard to go through" on the phone.  He offered no solutions, other than lowering my coverage. 

 He was helpful in letting me know that he could cancel my policy for me over the phone though...
